divs: Sighting DetailsI was putting out the trash and noticed red lights from the north, slightly above tree line. Watched lights appear one after another following the same direction. Ran inside grabbed my video cam and videotaped incident. Objects were not helicopters or planes, they were lights that changed shaped and disappeared in the same location. My feelings are the objects were UFO's (unidentified flying objects).
Summary: Plsating lights, approx 10, traveling same path rising and disappearing, I have footage
